OL,6,FA carer who sexually abused a disabled
OL,7,Fchild in his care has had his sentence
OL,8,Fmore than doubled by the Solicitor
OL,9,FGeneral.
OL,11,FJamil Talukder, 23, from Sheffield,
OL,12,Fstarted caring for the child in
OL,13,FOctober 2023 the year after moving to
OL,14,Fthe UK from Bangaladesh to study for a
OL,15,Fmarketing degree.
OL,17,FHe was caught on camera assaulting the
OL,18,Fvictim on several occasions after the
OL,19,Fmother of the child became suspicious
OL,20,Fand set up covert recording.
