OL,3,CCarer who sexually abused disabled
OL,4,Cchild has sentence increased
OL,6,FVictim personal statements reveal that
OL,7,Fthe child distrusts male carers since
OL,8,Fhis assault by Talukder.
OL,10,FThe court also heard that Talukder
OL,11,Fsexually abused another child and was
OL,12,Fcaught out when it was discovered that
OL,13,Fhe had recorded the abuse on his phone.
OL,15,FHe was jailed for three years at
OL,16,FSheffield Crown Court in February for
OL,17,Fsix sexual offences, but his sentence
OL,18,Fwas referred to the Court of Appeal
OL,19,Funder the Unduly Lenient Sentence
OL,20,Fscheme.
