OL,3,CCarer who sexually abused disabled
OL,4,Cchild has sentence increased
OL,6,FOn 22 May 2025, his sentence was
OL,7,Fincreased to eight years by the
OL,8,FSolicitor General Lucy Rigby KC MP.
OL,10,FShe said: "Jamil Talukder preyed on a
OL,11,Fvulnerable child he was meant to be
OL,12,Ftaking care of, as well as another
OL,13,Fyoung child.
OL,15,F"He abused the trust that was placed
OL,16,Fin him for his own sexual
OL,17,Fgratification, and I welcome the
OL,18,FCourt's increase to his sentence. I
OL,19,Fwould like to extend my sympathies to
OL,20,Fhis victims and their families."
